<li><a href="/wiki/Bertrand_Russell" title="Bertrand Russell">Bertrand Russell</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Friedrich_Schelling" title="Friedrich Schelling" class="mw-redirect">Friedrich Schelling</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Baruch_Spinoza" title="Baruch Spinoza">Baruch Spinoza</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/A.N._Whitehead" title="A.N. Whitehead" class="mw-redirect">A.N. Whitehead</a></li>
