</ul>
<p><a name="Asian_Philosophers_and_Teachers" id="Asian_Philosophers_and_Teachers"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Nondualism&amp;action=edit&amp;section=17" title="Edit section: Asian Philosophers and Teachers">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Asian Philosophers and Teachers</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Nagarjuna" title="Nagarjuna">Nagarjuna</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Adi_Sankara" title="Adi Sankara" class="mw-redirect">Shankaracharya</a></li>
